The Zondo Commission will hear Eskom related evidence from the former Eskom Head of Legal and Company Secretary, Suzanne Daniels. The Commission will also hear evidence from the former Eskom Senior Manager: Coal Sourcing, Nonhlanhla Kraai. Editors's note: Livestream courtesy #DStv403 #eNCA has ended. You may watch the recording above. JOHANNESBURG - The Zondo Commission will hear Eskom-related evidence from the former Eskom Head of Legal and Company Secretary Suzanne Daniels and the former Eskom Senior Manager Nonhlanhla Kraai.